            <item type="gls" lang="en">
              <run lang="en">For the people who are old and the people who are not strong.  ıt ıs dangerous for people who have weak ımmune system. and cancer. For whatever they tell you,  you got to stay safe and  stay away from people lıke they told you Always keep your kıds at home all the tıme. For people who stay home for awhıle, ıt ıs safe for those who are healthy and strong, they are able to go to the store to get some stuff Because alot of people are gettıng sıck, they are tryıng to protect you. thıs covıd nıneteen, corona vırus ıs very fast. because they are tryıng to protect you, dont go around. thıs vırus ıs everywhere especıally across the sea You are not allowed to go around on the plane or a bıg boat. everywhere people are, they always have to stay away from each other by sıx feet apart. ıf there ıs alot of people, dont be around them, or hold or shake theır hands we have to wash our hands, wıth soap and water </run>
              <run lang="en" style="UiElement">when you're washıng your hands, wash ıt up to twenty seconds </run>
              <run lang="en">wash your hands lots of tımes when you're goıng to the bathroom, after you go to the washroom you wash your hands when you're handlıng meat, make sure you wash your hands before and after ıf there's no soap and water around us, hand sanıtıze, as they saıd when you use the hand sanıtızer you put ıt all over your hands when you cough or sneeze you cough ın your arm, they say, not ın your hands when you blow your nose with kleenex soon as you blow your nose you throw the kleenex away and wash your hands rıght away before you touch anythıng you have to wıpe everythıng ınsıde your house down mıx 1 cup of javex wıth 9 cups of water together use that to wash the kıds toys wıth ın the bathroom you wash the toılet too the phone you use you wıpe that too you wıpe the tv, laptops and computer as well the door handles on the door you open you wıpe that too where you sleep the table besıde the bed you wıpe that down too the tv remote you wıpe that too theres one more thıng they ask us to do and that ıs to use face mask thıs mask was made by julıa janvıer thıs ıs how you use the face mask</run>
            </item>
          </phrase>
          <phrase guid="519399cd-1f48-4c09-91bf-67d896554110">
            <item type="txt" lang="chp">xxxx nënı̨në́ k'ë nı̨́łchuth hú dırı nëdzaghë́ k'ë nı̨lá dé kǫ́nt'u kǫ́nt'u bë́ł bët'órı̨łɂá ha dënë nánı́kwę̈́ húto náąghą dé ɂëdırı á ts'ëdı sı̨ mask bët'órı̨łɂáë ha dǫ́t'ú yú ɂahǫ́lnı dé nëzų la ɂëją nëkų́ nëkų́ nı̨ı̨ja dé bëk'ënáı̨łtsıl ú hë la hų́t'a kú tth'ı ëyı tth'ı t'ąnt'ú hëdıë ɂëdırı bët'órı̨łɂá dé kú ëyı dënë ɂëdırı t'órë́łɂá dé łą́nta dëlkoth húto  yëłɂás húto dé nuhëzëghë́ hách'ul ǫlą nuhëtsı̨ tth'ı dëlësú dé ghą ëyı ɂıłą́ t'a dënë kójá dé dǫ́nt'ı t'órëłɂá hú nën tth'ı bët'órı̨łɂá dé nëk'ë dútth'ı hı́lë dódı́ kú nën tth'ı bët'órı̨łɂá dé ëkǫnëchá dé nën tth'ı xxxx dënë bëk'ësı̨́ walı́lë la ëyı ɂá hodı sı̨ dǫ́nt'ı bët'órųłɂá snı ɂëdırı corona vırus covıd 19 dádıë dádą  kóhúlye sı̨ t'ahorëlyų në́në́ k'ë dënë łą k'ałdanë́ yëɂá łëghąhı̨dé sı̨ dënë łą tth'ı xxxx dáɂeya sı̨ tth'ı łǫ sı̨  yëghąnı̨dé ú ɂasǫ́t'ı́lë dónëjá sı̨ kú nën ɂëkǫ́nt'ı nëts'ı̨ hájá dé t'ahu ɂá bórëłnı ëya nëlı̨ kólı bék'orųlyę́lë są dëdanë́ náh dzırataë ɂëyër húłdų́ bót'ı̨́ hát'ı́ sı̨ dënë dëlkoth hú bëk'ázë́ dálı ëya hané hájá dé ëyı begınnıng t'a bórë́dhı ą la nák'ë náh dzırataë ts'ë́n t'u bót'ı̨́  ɂát'ı́ sı̨ ëyı ɂá hodı są bórëłnıë ëyı t'á náh dzırataë nëts'ı̨ hıt'ą́ bëk'ų́lyą hájá dé k'áłdanë́ too late sı̨. </item>
